{"article_id":"J4phhcfhZhVSPdNL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON --","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"There is plenty of political bad blood","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"flowing through our nation 's capital ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"but one relationship","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that could be described as the love-hate variety","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"is between President Donald Trump and the mainstream media .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"And here 's some `` real news '' :","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"President Trump likes going after the mainstream media ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"even calling them the `` enemy of the American people . ''","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Meanwhile , the opponent","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"-- in this case the mainstream press --","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"does n't mind punching back .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"`` We are not fake news , ''","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"said White House Correspondents ' Association President Jeff Mason .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"`` We are not failing news organizations","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and we are not the enemy of the American people . ''","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"The gloves came off at the president 's very first press conference , a testy affair","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"where Trump sparred with a few of them ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"exclaiming ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"`` The public does n't believe you people anymore ! ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"A Media Research Center study shows","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that 89 percent of the Trump coverage by the major media networks is negative .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Former campaign manager Corey Lewandowski told News","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"he believes","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"this treatment is intentional .","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"`` They want to highlight what they perceive to be failures , ''","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"Lewandowski said .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"`` This is exactly what they did during the campaign .","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"They said","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"the president would never run ,","depth":16},{"id":30,"text":"that he would never be successful ,","depth":17},{"id":31,"text":"the campaign was in shambles , ''","depth":17},{"id":32,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"`` But it was n't , ''","depth":16},{"id":34,"text":"he continued .","depth":16},{"id":35,"text":"`` It was n't sophisticated enough .","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"But the American people stepped up","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"and said ,","depth":17},{"id":38,"text":"'we want Donald Trump","depth":17},{"id":39,"text":"and voted for him . ' ''","depth":16},{"id":40,"text":"Lewandowski says","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"all","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"the president wants is a fair shake and the whole story to be told .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"`` When he does a long interview with a major publication like The New York Times or The Wall Street Journal","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"all","depth":16},{"id":45,"text":"he asks for","depth":16},{"id":46,"text":"is do n't edit it .","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"Just print it verbatim","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"if you do that","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"he believes that to be a fair interview , ''","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"he told News .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` I agree with him .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"It 's when they cut it up ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"chop it up","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"and they do n't run the full context of what he 's saying","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"is usually where the media perpetuates a narrative","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"that is n't true for the president , ''","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"There has been plenty pushback from the mainstream media team .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"`` He loves the media in many ways as much","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"as he hates it , ''","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Paul Farhi , the media reporter for The Washington Post , told News .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"`` I think","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Trump makes a very big show","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"of disliking us ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"disrespecting us","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"and disparaging us ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"but I think","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"in fact secretly , or maybe not so secretly , really likes us , ''","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Farhi said ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"`` loves the attention ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"has used that attention for his own advancement","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and has really courted the media in a lot of ways . ''","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Trump courts the media ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"using handwritten notes","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"to either praise or blast them .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"But whatever the case , Farhi says","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"he definitely works the room .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"`` Trump is a very sophisticated media animal , ''","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Farhi told News .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"`` He has worked with the New York media ,","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"which is the most intense","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"for decades .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"He knows his way around","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"and he knows how to utilize the media","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"to get his message out . ''","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"The question now is will we continue to see this daily soap opera drama play out the next four years ?","depth":3},{"id":88,"text":"Jake Sherman with Politico told News","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"there 's no reason","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"to believe","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"anything will be different .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"`` Donald Trump is 70 years old , ''","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"he noted .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"`` He 's not going to change ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"so","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"if we 're looking for some sort of major course correction or a major shift in dynamic ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"we 're not going to get that .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"He is who he is","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"and you 're not going to change that at this point in the game . ''","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"The one thing","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Trump may look to change","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"is the country 's libel and slander laws","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"to make it easier to sue reporters and media outlets over their stories .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"That could be the next level in an escalating fight with no end in sight .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":0,"right":208,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":208,"left":190,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":112,"right":189,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":112,"left":109,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":106,"right":108,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":6,"right":110,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":110,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":114,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":113,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":161,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":160,"right":59,"relation":"advers